    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I face the same issue from Java application built in Jdevelopr 11.1.1.7 IDE. I solved the issue by unchecking the use of proxy form Project properties.</p>\n\n<p>You can find it in the following:\nProject Properties -> (from left panle )Run/Debug/Profile ->Click (edit) form the right panel -> Tool Setting from the left panel -> uncheck (Use Proxy) option.</p>\n"
