    "creation_date" : 1486414035,
    "answer_id" : 42077000,
    "question_id" : 6532273,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Adding this as an answer as it might help someone later.</p>\n\n<p>I had to force jvm to use the IPv4 stack to resolve the error. My application used to work within company network, but while connecting from home it gave the same exception. No proxy involved. Added the jvm argument \n   <code>-Djava.net.preferIPv4Stack=true</code> and all the <code>https</code> requests were behaving normally.</p>\n"
