    "answer_id" : 49458519,
    "question_id" : 6532273,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was facing this exception when using Gmail.</p>\n\n<p>In order to use Gmail I had to <strong>turn ON \"Allow less secure apps\"</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>This Gmail setting can be found at <a href=\"https://www.google.com/settings/security/lesssecureapps\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://www.google.com/settings/security/lesssecureapps</a> after login the gmail account.</p>\n"
