    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>i solved my problem using port 25 and Following prop</p>\n\n<pre><code>mailSender.javaMailProperties.putAll([\n                \"mail.smtp.auth\": \"true\",\n                \"mail.smtp.starttls.enable\": \"false\",\n                \"mail.smtp.ssl.enable\": \"false\",\n                \"mail.smtp.socketFactory.fallback\": \"true\",\n        ]);\n</code></pre>\n"
