    "question_id" : 6532273,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In case you use Jetty version 9 or earlier you need to add it to jetty\nby</p>\n<pre><code>RUN java -jar ${JETTY_HOME}/start.jar --add-to-startd=https\n</code></pre>\n<p>and according to this\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33146476/jetty-how-to-use-ssl-in-jetty-client-side\">Jetty: How to use SSL in Jetty client side</a></p>\n<p>from Jetty version 10 it should work out of the box</p>\n"
  }, {
